               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 2</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBering\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBering', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">A map showing Indigenous migration routes across the Bering Strait. Photo taken at the Museo Nacional de Antropología en San Salvador, El Salvador (<htcite0>), on <htdate0>.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Who truly discovered America (<i>Abya Yala</i>)? (Who... ?)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 2</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Babylonian world map © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite1>) superimposed on the modern world map © Mapswire (<htcite2>). Shariing under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a> license.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>America: Inca (Tawantinsuyu) (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>America: Mesoamerica (Different Frontiers) (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>America: Mesoamerica (The Beginning) (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>America: Minas Gerais (BR) (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Bantu Expansion (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Comparing Worlds (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Continent: