('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Surface Coordinates (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>The Ancient Babylonian World Map (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>The Size of the Earth (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Where are we on a sphere? (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Where is the center? (<a href=\"index.html?page=atlas\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('atlas','html', '', false); return false;\">Atlas</a>)</li><li>Our Week (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Understanding the Multiplication Tables (Summary) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Modulating (Part I) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps_volume2\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps_volume2','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 2)</a>)</li><li>Modulating (Part II) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps_volume2\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps_volume2','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 2)</a>)</li><li>Modulating (Part III) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps_volume2\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps_volume2','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 2)</a>)</li><li>Chronology (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Cradles of civilization (Part I) (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Cradles of civilization (Parte II) (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Culture and Civilization (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Anachronism (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Equality Levels (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Fractionating Texts (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>The Writing System (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Yupana (Multiplication) (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Did texts written in Mesopotamia describe the world we know today? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>Did the Indigenous peoples lack the knowledge and technology to build pyramids? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>Has there never been a flood? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>Expanding... (Universe)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
